data.description: Come enjoy 3.8 acres in Bosque NM. This  great horse property is set up with 4 large corrals with water to each corral. Has a  covered barn/ tack room for hay and your tools. This home is a 3 bed 2 bath with pro panel roof. It has been well maintained and is  ready for you to move in. Book your showing today.
